verse.lines:
{lang-eng}Yesuni chetulandu yesuni rommunan naaku nabhayamandu
Nande parundedan dootalu paaduchundu paatanu
Vintivaa naayana yandundi pondu sukhambahaa !{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Yesuni chethulandu mikkili kshemamu ye dukhabaadalaina
Nachata cheravu paapapu bheethi baadhalantavu
Nannitan kanneeru sandiyambul konni dinaallitan{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Yese naa yaashrayambu naaka chaavondegaa golgotha
Yandu nundu naa guri sarvadaa cheekati daatudaaka
Norputho nundedan jereda ninka naaka manchunu nammedan{/lang-eng}
